sequenceDiagram
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Operator as mlflow-operator<br/>controller-runtime
    participant Helm as Helm Renderer<br/>(in-process)
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Gateway as data-science-gateway<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Pod<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS (service-ca)
    participant DB as PostgreSQL/MySQL<br/>5432/3306 TCP
    participant S3 as S3-compatible Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Prom as Prometheus

    Note over K8sAPI,Operator: Flow 1: MLflow CR Reconciliation
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch event: MLflow CR created/updated<br/>HTTPS/6443 | TLS 1.2+ | SA Token
    Operator->>Helm: Render chart with CR spec as values<br/>(in-process, no network)
    Helm-->>Operator: Rendered K8s manifests
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Server-side apply: Deployment, Service,<br/>HTTPRoute, ConsoleLink, NetworkPolicy, RBAC<br/>HTTPS/6443 | TLS 1.2+ | SA Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update MLflow CR status<br/>HTTPS/6443 | TLS 1.2+ | SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Status updated

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 2: MLflow Client Request via Gateway API
    Client->>Gateway: POST /mlflow/api/2.0/...<br/>HTTPS/443 | TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token (K8s)
    Gateway->>MLflow: Forward (path rewrite: /mlflow/api → /api)<br/>HTTPS/8443 | TLS (service-ca) | Passthrough
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS/6443 | TLS 1.2+ | Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Access decision (allow/deny)
    MLflow->>DB: Query/store metadata<br/>5432 or 3306/TCP | DB wire protocol<br/>TLS verify-full (when CA configured)<br/>Connection string credentials
    DB-->>MLflow: Query results
    MLflow->>S3: Store/retrieve artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 or HTTP/9000<br/>TLS 1.2+ | S3 credentials from secret
    S3-->>MLflow: Artifact data
    MLflow-->>Gateway: JSON Response
    Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Prom,MLflow: Flow 3: Prometheus Metrics Scraping
    Prom->>Prom: ServiceMonitor discovery
    Prom->>MLflow: GET /metrics<br/>HTTPS/8443 | TLS (service-ca verified<br/>via openshift-service-ca.crt)<br/>Bearer Token
    MLflow-->>Prom: Prometheus metrics
